full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/1/2023 CA No. 36325174 Personal description of holder USCIS Registration No. A026271163 as of date of naturalization: I certify that the description given is true, and that the photograph affixced Date of birth: NOVEMBER 08, 1910 hereto is a likeness of me.
